originalText.text: Nigel Borel was wonderful to work with. He took the time to understand my particular circumstances and led me through the process to land a lovely apartment. Always upfront and communicative. Highly recommended!

originalText.text: I got the pleasure of running across Moss Realty and working with Nigel Borel. Very kind, honest and professional broker. After working with so many agents, Nigel by far gave me the best service I had encountered. Nigel was prompt, efficient, had great communication, and was very organized. I love the property's he works with and very happy with my place and the process... honestly I can't tell you enough what Nigel did for me during a very stressful time. What a help and pleasure he was to work with. I highly recommend Moss Realty and especially Nigel. I have passed his information on to several people.

originalText.text: Working with Nigel was fantastic. He was very responsive, pleasant and clear about the process. Naturally he offered a lot of information about the building/unit I was looking at but he also knew a lot about the neighborhood and its history, which I really appreciated. I felt respected as a person -not just a potential renter- during our exchange. I love my apartment and 10 out of 10 would recommend him.

originalText.text: I recently had the pleasure of working with Moss Realty to find a new flat near the Columbia Campus. Nigel, my broker, provided excellent service throughout the entire process, and I was very satisfied with the level of responsiveness and support he provided. The location of the flat is superb, with easy access to the university and surrounding area. Moss Realty offers great value for the price of their flats, and I was very happy with the quality of the living space I was able to secure within my budget. Overall, I highly recommend Moss Realty for anyone who is looking for a reliable and professional real estate company in the area.
